== Gewinner und Nominierte ==

=== Bester Film ===

'''[[Lebenskünstler (Film)|Lebenskünstler]] ''(You Can’t Take It with You)'' – [[Frank Capra]]'''

: [[Robin Hood, König der Vagabunden]] ''(The Adventures of Robin Hood)'' – [[Hal B. Wallis]], [[Henry Blanke]]
: [[Alexander's Ragtime Band (Film)|Alexander's Ragtime Band]] ''(Alexander's Ragtime Band)'' – [[Darryl F. Zanuck]], [[Harry Joe Brown]]
: [[Teufelskerle]] ''(Boys Town)'' – [[John W. Considine Jr.]]
: [[Die Zitadelle]] ''(The Citadel)'' – [[Victor Saville]]
: [[Vater dirigiert]] ''(Four Daughters)'' – [[Hal B. Wallis]], [[Henry Blanke]]
: [[Die große Illusion]] ''(La Grande illusion)'' – [[Frank Rollmer]], [[Albert Pinkovitch]]
: [[Jezebel – Die boshafte Lady]] ''(Jezebel)'' – [[Hal B. Wallis]], [[Henry Blanke]]
: [[Pygmalion: Der Roman eines Blumenmädchens]] ''(Pygmalion)'' – [[Gabriel Pascal]]
: [[Der Testpilot]] ''(Test Pilot)'' – [[Louis D. Lighton]]

